            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "廣州南站35歲男持水果刀傷人　一人受傷送醫",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"廣州南站。中新社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c89f62f34c8f0a0ba064084af4827f86/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051520424073057.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">廣州南站。中新社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>官方通報，一名男子今日（15日）在廣州南站持刀傷人，造成一人受傷。目前案件正在進一步偵辦中。\n\n</p>\n<p>廣州鐵路公安局廣州公安處官方微博今日發布警情通報稱，廣州南站一樓西北區（安檢區外）當天下午2時許發生一起持水果刀傷人案件。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"官方發佈通報。廣州鐵路公安處\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/136e52364e2e0958a653bbf137bb9ee5/2025-05/xkw75MIuFZt8eN4nZyf9NydrO8fEPx_UzhoGL84aBi8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        官方發佈通報。廣州鐵路公安處\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>通報稱，民警及時到場處置，將35歲的李姓犯罪嫌疑人當場控制。案件造成一人受傷，傷者已及時送醫救治，無生命危險。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069130/即時-中國-廣州南站35歲男持水果刀傷人-一人受傷送醫",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 20:51:22",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "11歲童私院切扁桃腺口內遺留紗布  消息指涉聖德肋撒醫院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"11歲童私院切扁桃腺口內遺留紗布 消息指涉聖德肋撒醫院\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/31b87c86e56f413d3e9c7dd10aa989a8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051520395681285.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">11歲童私院切扁桃腺口內遺留紗布 消息指涉聖德肋撒醫院</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>私院再爆醫療事故。衞生署私營醫療機構規管辦公室於今年3月，接獲私家醫院呈報了一宗「醫療風險警示事件」，涉及一名接受扁桃腺及腺樣體切除術的11歲男病人，有紗布被遺留在口腔內。今年第一季辦公室另收到私家醫院呈報一宗涉及錯誤處方藥物的重要風險事件，涉及向一名病人注射化療藥物時輸液速度出錯。據了解，涉及醫療風險警示的醫院為聖德肋撒醫院，涉及重要風險事件的醫院為養和醫院。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250778/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"養和醫院。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8dbc5cb2a2de232f2b1bfdb69e88e7c/2025-05/DNSG1202HKSH001.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        養和醫院。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250779/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"養和醫院。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/337eb20c1c8631d1cdfac1007d7722cb/2025-05/DNSG1202HKSH002.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        養和醫院。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250780/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"聖德肋撒醫院。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5650ca3fd5c4f9e2a3220ef27580da48/2025-05/NR250514STH34.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        聖德肋撒醫院。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250781/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"聖德肋撒醫院。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c4a150f5681d02e47a71fb0f4cc2f1b/2025-05/NR250514STH36.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        聖德肋撒醫院。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250808/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0190bd26af7973591f716788a350c73/2025-05/051512013215.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>衞生署回覆《星島頭條》指，涉及醫療風險警示事件的11歲男病人，其後已將紗布吐出，現已出院。此外，涉及今年第一季錯誤處方藥物的重要風險事件的60歲女病人，情況未有受事件影響。有關私家醫院在識別事件後24小時內呈報。衞生署在收到呈報後隨即作出跟進，並要求有關私家醫院於四周內提交調查報告。有關私家醫院已向衞生署提交調查報告。\n\n</p>\n<p>衞生署指，就上述重要風險事件，署方未有發現證據顯示醫院在房舍、人手、設備方面，違反《私營醫療機構條例》（第633章）或相關實務守則適用的要求，而導致出現重要風險事件。醫療風險警示事件的調查仍在進行中，有關私家醫院均已採取改善措施。衞生署會繼續監察私家醫院實施相關措施的情況。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：趙克平\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069129/即時-港聞-11歲童私院切扁桃腺口內遺留紗布-消息指涉聖德肋撒醫院",
