        {
            "title": "仁滙醫務｜消委會接1120宗投訴  涉款591萬元  最高金額個案逾3.9萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"仁滙醫務｜消委會接1120宗投訴  涉款591萬元 。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/95db74391f185cc51a9b8cc86eac95c8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051520352845377.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">仁滙醫務｜消委會接1120宗投訴  涉款591萬元 。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>提供嬰幼兒疫苗注射的仁滙醫務集團懷疑結業，大批家長求助。消委會今日（15日）表示，截至今午5時，消委會共接獲1120宗有關仁滙懷疑結業的投訴，涉及金額合共約591萬元，當中涉最高金額的個案為39960元，每宗個案平均金額為5277元。\n\n</p>\n<p>消委會續指，按投訴性質分類，涉及「店舖結業」佔最多，共1045宗；其次為「更改/終止合約」，共53宗；涉「服務延誤」和「銷售手法」性質的分別則有9宗和7宗。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069128/即時-港聞-仁滙醫務-消委會接1120宗投訴-涉款591萬元-最高金額個案逾3-9萬元",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-15 20:46:19",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黎諾懿未落實赴大馬拍劇︰乜都爭少少  賴慰玲最叻揀象拔蚌︰要訣係又粗又長",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/ebf8eac1d2584564db56aab10bf9f0b2/2025-05/page_210.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/2002ae1b318771f0873d36a5e8aa0102/15a56a91469f43a4b3c2886681d32e95-b772a57466b30f1502724dd5fb975143-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6825de98270c3\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6825de98270c5\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎諾懿未落實赴大馬拍劇︰乜都爭少少  賴慰玲學識劏魚最叻揀象拔蚌︰要訣係又粗又長\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bee6d0f7273ae0e264bd5e2ed8896b19/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051520230924064.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎諾懿未落實赴大馬拍劇︰乜都爭少少  賴慰玲學識劏魚最叻揀象拔蚌︰要訣係又粗又長</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>黎諾㦤、賴慰玲、劉穎鏇、吳偉豪出席《一日打工限定》記者會。黎諾㦤與賴慰玲分別體驗兩餸飯店員和魚販打工，賴慰玲自認不入廚房的人，今次在節目中學識了劏魚，已不會驚，又指自己最叻揀象拔蚌，要訣是揀「又粗又長」。\n\n</p><h2>黎諾㦤有潔癖</h2>\n<p>黎諾㦤體驗的工種，看似輕鬆，他直言有難處，初時以為可以歎檸茶，見到廚師獨自應付50多道菜好忙，又要企足全日，自認最叻是和街坊打牙骹。問可想體驗「渠王」？賴慰玲稱怕臭，黎諾㦤自認有潔癖，沾到污水會不開心一整天。問到是否將到馬來西亞拍劇？黎諾㦤指未能透露，「乜都爭少少，下次可能可以講，可能去兩個月，可能有15集！」黎諾㦤與賴慰玲表示想合作，拍《魚販和兩餸飯愛情故事》。賴慰玲升呢為藝員訓練班導師，她表示開心和同事一齊研究演技，大家好踴躍，有20、30人報名，當中以倪樂琳最有天份，黎諾㦤則指自己都有報名但賴慰玲不教他。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3446724/%E6%9D%8E%E4%BD%B3%E8%8A%AF%E5%AD%96%E9%BB%8E%E8%AB%BE%E6%87%BF%E6%8B%8D%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%AB%E5%8A%87-%E5%8B%A4%E7%B7%B4%E6%AD%8C%E6%83%B3%E5%94%B1%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2-%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%A2%AB%E5%8B%95%E6%8B%8D%E6%8B%96%E9%9D%A0%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%A9\">李佳芯孖黎諾懿拍大馬黑幫劇 勤練歌想唱主題曲 性格被動拍拖靠個天</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250674/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎諾㦤、劉穎鏇、賴慰玲與吳偉豪在將軍澳電視城出席《一日打工限定》記者會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22e84fef53a34079c6ebc7bd98df768d/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_50_1__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎諾㦤、劉穎鏇、賴慰玲與吳偉豪在將軍澳電視城出席《一日打工限定》記者會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250302/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有指黎諾㦤再與李佳芯拍劇，他表示時機未成熟，「唔講得住」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f2dd51a6449f329a6634e12165a726e/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_47.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有指黎諾㦤再與李佳芯拍劇，他表示時機未成熟，「唔講得住」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250303/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎諾㦤與賴慰玲賴慰玲拍節目學識劏魚，指自己最叻揀象拔蚌，「又粗又長最好」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82507d6dca23e92f218c02181db47887/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_48.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎諾㦤與賴慰玲賴慰玲拍節目學識劏魚，指自己最叻揀象拔蚌，「又粗又長最好」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250308/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇  賴慰玲  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17f2d0dd22b48b131cab192245b57913/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_51_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉穎鏇  賴慰玲  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250310/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《一日打工限定》得影后龔嘉欣玩dirty嘢。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce84823372cb3fe731c9268be791381b/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_52_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《一日打工限定》得影后龔嘉欣玩dirty嘢。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250311/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎諾㦤  吳偉豪\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6fb45562dd2d729d662255cd32fa9cca/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_52.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎諾㦤  吳偉豪\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250323/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎諾懿與賴慰玲都對厭惡性工作耍手擰頭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd0a2b1fbef3cf64ce21dc4264b9b2ca/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_58_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎諾懿與賴慰玲都對厭惡性工作耍手擰頭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250328/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黎諾㦤與賴慰玲表示想合作，拍《魚販和兩餸飯愛情故事》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2257606f2051f9dcca152b873c8613a/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_05_00_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黎諾㦤與賴慰玲表示想合作，拍《魚販和兩餸飯愛情故事》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
